## 처리 유형

### ZERO_UNRECOGNIZED (사전 미등록)
→ search_keywords에 INSERT
```sql
-- 예시
INSERT INTO search_keywords (keyword, keyword_type, category_main, priority, is_deleted, is_recommended, allow_rising)
VALUES ('린넨셔츠', 'CATEGORY', 'TOP', 50, false, false, true)
ON CONFLICT (keyword) DO NOTHING;
```

### ZERO_NO_MATCH (사전 있지만 매칭 상품 없음)
→ search_keyword_relations에 SIMILAR 관계 INSERT
```sql
-- 예시
INSERT INTO search_keyword_relations (source_keyword_id, target_keyword_id, relation_type, relation_score)
SELECT s.id, t.id, 'SIMILAR', 0.8
FROM search_keywords s, search_keywords t
WHERE s.keyword = '청바지' AND t.keyword = '데님팬츠'
ON CONFLICT (source_keyword_id, target_keyword_id) DO NOTHING;
```

